{"tid":2049673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國真攬炒系列: 美國示威逾9千人被捕　教宗稱不能對種族歧視視而不見","createTime":"2020-06-03T15:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T23:10:40.000Z","uid":292292,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b598e30af512994ccec25442a1a16d8da7cf251","tid":2049673,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530026-20200603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530026-20200603.htm&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=0cd5acba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530026-20200603.htm&h=46a28f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530026-20200603.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子弗洛伊德死亡後，引發不滿警方的全國示威持續。<br />\n<br />\n多個城市連續第八晚都有民眾上街，有些城市的示威者是不理會宵禁令繼續抗議。<br />\n<br />\n紐約市的宵禁延長至星期日，並提早在晚上8時開始實施。<br />\n<br />\n五角大樓調動1600名士兵到華盛頓地區戒備。<br />\n<br />\n連日來全國的示威，至少9300人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n教宗方濟各首次回應事件，說不能對種族歧視視而不見。"},{"pid":"ae80297f4afa5afc84b89846ad2a87844f9c34a0","tid":2049673,"uid":81052,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"見唔見共產黨點對天主教徒?"},{"pid":"6184d978ed3a41b8d9a48159a926d1318711dcb1","tid":2049673,"uid":34065,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 方濟各 香港呢?香港人權自由呢?<br />\n我唔係怨婦跪求阿 我係屌班道德撚雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb243c1b38f338f79eda13cdac2ed980b3e86bb","tid":2049673,"uid":34065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae80297f4afa5afc84b89846ad2a87844f9c34a0","tid":2049673,"uid":81052,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"見唔見共產黨點對天主教徒?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"見撚到咩 支那直接拆埋佢個十字架都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/face